{"tid":1063634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范冰冰出現了！暴瘦藏不住黑眼圈 憔悴模樣曝光","createTime":"2019-03-16T02:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T05:33:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da4f40da752393f56adc4b831b51c3a9aa40c458","tid":1063634,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"中國女星范冰冰因逃稅掀起軒然大波，最後補繳約40億新台幣的稅金才免除刑事責任。事件落幕至今已數月，但她仍未正式出現在大眾面前，今（15）日有人貼出范冰冰的近照，憔悴模樣與過去判若兩人。<br />\n<br />\n有人在微博貼出與范冰冰的合照，只見范冰冰綁著低馬尾，身穿紫色上衣，塗了鮮紅色的口紅，臉上的妝非常淡，雖然已開了很強的美肌，仍擋不住范冰冰深深的黑眼圈。<br />\n<br />\n范冰冰與過去相比瘦了一大圈，臉小了一號，看起來有些憔悴，與原先霸氣十足的女王氣場大不相同。粉絲們紛紛表示「冰冰姐瘦好多喔」、「好好休息啊，黑眼圈都遮不住了」，並希望她能快點回歸演藝圈，不過也有人嗆「逃稅一生黑」、「還有臉回來撈錢啊」，引起兩面爭論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OunmJYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOunmJYO.jpg&h=18bfec64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p890Zw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp890Zw8.jpg&h=2f9d8e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPsEw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPsEw9.jpg&h=c74dcaa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"637fff37784c4d25b4819cbeab331851a33e7afb","tid":1063634,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩變到咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dc2e54e73b9a63b67347fd8971311ac2041734","tid":1063634,"uid":58630,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"同平時搭火車啲大陸妹一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4787a1f2b94d791390138269dfced37f3c71e6f2","tid":1063634,"uid":29093,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"表面就用錢解決 <br />\n枱底就用個閪解決 <br />\n<br />\n畀班幹部搞到殘哂"},{"pid":"720fd8e942ff8fc3728014f00d0421aec2e29930","tid":1063634,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":